Title: Livestatus Error when searching with wildcards in multisite
Component: multisite
Class: nastiness
State: done
Date: 2012-09-24 10:51:47
Targetversion: future

A Search with wildcards in the quicksearch, leads to:
Livestatus problem: Unhandled exception: 400: error in Filter header: invalid regular expression '*omd*'

2012-10-04 16:34:59: changed state open -> done
The quicksearch text is converted to regex ( * -> .* ) when using livestatus
